Simple DungeonGenerator explanation
generateDungeon(): Main method to generate the dungeon layout.
generateRooms(): Creates multiple rooms with random positions and sizes.
generateHallways(): Connects the rooms with hallways.
generateSafeZones(): Adds safe zones at random positions.
populateMap(): Adds all the generated tiles to the map.
The Map class is used to render the map after generation


